<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM5.3.1">
<l>mācaṟu cōtiyeṉ ceyya vāymaṇik kuṉṟattai</l>
<l>yācaṟu cīlaṉai yāti mūrttiyai nāṭiyē</l>
<l>pācaṟa veyti yaṟiviḻan teṉainā ḷaiya</l>
<l>mēcaṟu mūravar kavvai tōḻī yeṉceyyumē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>How many our days, knowledge lost, reaching the end of [our] fresh colour,</l>
<l>just seeking the primordial form, the man of faultless character,</l>
<l>our sapphire hill with red mouth, the spotless light?</l>
<l>The gossip of the troubled villagers, friend, what will it do?</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
